      • CRAFTING

        public static final InventoryArchetype CRAFTING
        A Players personal crafting area. Output with 2x2 Grid

      • CHEST

        public static final InventoryArchetype CHEST
        A Chest. Sizes from 9x1 to 9x6 are allowed. The default is 9x3.

        When displaying the inventory the actual arrangement of slot does not matter. This means, that when creating a 3x3 CHEST inventory it will still be displayed as 9x1 to the player.

      • DOUBLE_CHEST

        public static final InventoryArchetype DOUBLE_CHEST
        A DoubleChest. Sizes 9x1 to 9x6 are allowed. The default is 9x6.

      • HOPPER

        public static final InventoryArchetype HOPPER
        A Hopper. The size is always 5x1

      • DISPENSER

        public static final InventoryArchetype DISPENSER
        A Dispenser or Dropper. The size is always 3x3

      • WORKBENCH

        public static final InventoryArchetype WORKBENCH
        A Workbench. The size is always 3x3 + 1 OutputSlot

      • FURNACE

        public static final InventoryArchetype FURNACE
        A Furnace. The size is always 3 slots

      • ENCHANTING_TABLE

        public static final InventoryArchetype ENCHANTING_TABLE
        A EnchantingTable. The size is always 2 slots.

      • ANVIL

        public static final InventoryArchetype ANVIL
        A Anvil. The size is always 3 slots.

      • BREWING_STAND

        public static final InventoryArchetype BREWING_STAND
        A BrewingStand. 5 Slots.

      • BEACON

        public static final InventoryArchetype BEACON
        A Beacon. The size is always one slot.

      • HORSE

        public static final InventoryArchetype HORSE
        A RideableHorse, Donkey or Mule usually 2 Slots.

      • VILLAGER

        public static final InventoryArchetype VILLAGER
        A Villager. The size is always 3 slots.

      • HORSE_WITH_CHEST

        public static final InventoryArchetype HORSE_WITH_CHEST
        A Donkey or Mule with Chest. 2 Slots and 5x3 Chest Needs a horse as carrier to show to player in Vanilla.

      • PLAYER

        public static final InventoryArchetype PLAYER
        A Player. Includes 9x3 main inventory, 9x1 Hotbar, 4 Armorslots and 2x2 Crafting area.

        Cannot be opened by the server in Vanilla.

      • UNKNOWN

        public static final InventoryArchetype UNKNOWN
